{
  "stem": "13141.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So back and forth, by the time you were answered, it was a matter of, of almost three months.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it, it was very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You could send telegrams with 10 words.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But again, to send a telegram, you needed all kinds of authorizations and filing from the Gestapo, you know, to send a telegram.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is correct.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By letter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We communicated by letter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you, you were already afraid to write everything the way you felt because you were never sure whether letters were not opened.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most likely, they were not at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then in 1940-- don't forget, in 1940 and 1941-- Germany entered the war in 1939, September 1st, 1939, when, when they-- when they attacked Poland.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before, of course, there was the Anschluss of Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was the invasion in, in, in, Sudetenland, in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But since the Czech never put up any resistance, since they were let down by the-- by France and by England, even though they had a pact, a non-aggression pact.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when they were being attacked by the Germans, the, the Frenchmen didn't do anything, and the English didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [LAUGHS] my father sold what they had taken along.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had taken all the, the household goods along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had eight rooms in, in, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still have two chairs left upstairs, big wooden chairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father sold-- it was-- some were very fine things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had a, a big-- a big piano.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What do you call them, the-- with the-- these-- concert pianos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so my father, he started selling piece by piece.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lived off this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then my father, he did some commission business there, but everything [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] unofficially.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
